  defaultReply: The main source? Well, I think I'd do alright.
  replyKey:
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: a5e031b4b8ad96643858c00f5b5b1358, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4feb4edd41012224b88c5182159e2aa9, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 0a6c1ab90feb8be408dcb30f169ac47a, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 0fd171517e1147a4398fc997692f8f0e, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 138db3ffc7861704d8012aa6e86b9a09, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 65b960290032cc048a02be92fc50ee7c, type: 2}
  replyText:
  - Ah yes, that would be perfect for me! I couldn't think of anything else better
    suiting.
  - As long as it's romance, I will gladly be the protagonist!
  - If I could sing, of course! Singers are usually the main focus if they are included
    anyways.
  - Main role, side role, whatever. But my skills would greatly suffice.
  - That means I'm allowed to talk a lot, right? Then of course!
  - Of course... for someone as brooding like me, that is the only fitting role...
